name: AtomSDKAnalytics
description:
AtomSDKAnalytics provides Third Party Analytics integration for AtomSDK via the AtomAnalyticsProvider protocol.
This module allows you to enable analytics tracking in AtomSDK by providing an Analytics-based
implementation of the analytics provider interface.

This is an optional module - AtomSDK works perfectly fine without it, but analytics events
will be silently ignored if no provider is set.
